    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong>Vapor World: Over The Mind（蒸汽世界）是一款 2D 动作冒险游戏。受《只狼》和《血源诅咒》所启发，游戏融合了超现实主义的故事，迷雾般的美术氛围以及紧张刺激的高难度战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直面内心深处的恐怖梦魇</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你是一个失去记忆的神秘少年，误入了陌生的黑暗噩梦。这一切似乎与名为“Vapor World”的秘密项目有关，据说它成功实现了梦境的实体化，然而巨大的危机随之共同到来。为了解开背后的秘密，重回现实，你将踏上不惧死亡的冒险。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203010/extras/78465167dc4a18a13972a2097cfe54c2.avif?t=1772111062\" width=620 height=105 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的角色、敌人与场景全部为手绘，并具有独特的艺术风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时通过动态视角及光影设置，赋予2D游戏3D的空间立体感和极高的沉浸感</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203010/extras/b9d556ae1598cab3400986600cfb28d5.poster.avif?t=1772111062\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203010/extras/b9d556ae1598cab3400986600cfb28d5.webm?t=1772111062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203010/extras/b9d556ae1598cab3400986600cfb28d5.mp4?t=1772111062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203010/extras/956057d5c0a4f987cb5e84317c5fc28a.avif?t=1772111062\" width=620 height=105 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏有超过50种强敌和15个BOSS，每个都有独特的招式，并在各自的地盘守卫着被隐藏的秘密</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战它们绝非易事，你需要熟悉它们的招式，招架住它们的致命攻击，并拼尽全力才可能获胜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203010/extras/a4a4364be5438a4324a8c48c9f937763.avif?t=1772111062\" width=620 height=105 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败特殊敌人获取道具、消耗经验学习全新技能，探索世界带来的收获能让你在战斗更好的招架攻击或致盲敌人，从而得以更加轻松的击败它们</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203010/extras/50f184b2d2ba25949785f3560e7c0895.poster.avif?t=1772111062\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203010/extras/50f184b2d2ba25949785f3560e7c0895.webm?t=1772111062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203010/extras/50f184b2d2ba25949785f3560e7c0895.mp4?t=1772111062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203010/extras/2846ba2bf8307f45ea991f76bd945f40.avif?t=1772111062\" width=620 height=105 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用环境隐蔽自身，进行潜行刺杀。从而避免陷入到腹背受敌的苦战中，巧妙地击败群聚的敌人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203010/extras/b1cad49b31b04a482f717253e3d3853f.avif?t=1772111062\" width=620 height=105 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攀爬、跳跃、打破障碍或利用场景中的特定物品，一个超现实主义的梦中世界等待着您的互动与探索</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
